The evidence with the title 'Rajiv Satyal - Cape Town Comedy ClubCape Town Comedy Club ' says Rajiv has performed on three continents. He co-created the world-touring Make Chai Not War , a Hindu/Muslim stand-up show. The U.S. State Dept. sponsored it, sending it to seven cities in India . The show became part of the Congressional Record after being mentioned on Capitol Hill to secretaries of state Hillary Clinton  ... 
